<text corresp="#Cc" xml:lang="sa"> <body>
            <milestone n="454" unit="page"/>
            <head xml:lang="en"><lb n="19"/>5558</head>
            <head xml:lang="en"><lb n="20"/>Vināyaka Bhaṭṭa (Karpaṭa)</head>
            <head type="sub" xml:lang="en"><lb n="21"/>6024. <foreign xml:lang="sa">khaḍgaśatakam |</foreign> <hi rend="italic">Khadga-satakam</hi></head>
            <p xml:lang="en">
            <lb n="22"/>Substance, foolscap paper. 11 x 4½ inches Folia, 19 Lines, 7 on a <lb n="23"/>page. Extent in ślokas, 300. Character, very modern Nāgara. Appear<lb n="24"/>ance, fresh. Complete.
            </p>
            <p xml:lang="en">
            <lb n="25"/>A century of verses in honour of Kṛṣṇa's sword.
            </p>
            <p xml:lang="en">
            <lb n="26"/>Beginning :—
            </p>
            <p xml:lang="sa">
            <lb n="27"/>śrīgaṇeśāya namaḥ |
            </p>
            <div n="1">
                <lg type="verse" xml:id="v_1">
                    <l>
<lb n="28"/>kalpātikrūrakālabhrukuṭikuṭilatākalpakalpāgramuṣṭiḥ
<caesura/>
<lb n="29"/>krudhyatkālīkaṭākṣāṅkita iva kalayat kāntim ekāntakālīm |
                    </l>
                    <l>
<pb n="455" facs="480"/>
                      <lb n="1"/>krīḍaty asyākrameṇa krakacakṛtikṛtī kumbhikumbhāgrakūṭaḥ
<caesura/>
<lb n="2"/>kroḍe phutkṛttakaṇṭhojjhitarudhirakaṇākīrṇakoṇaḥ kṛpāṇaḥ ||
                    </l>
                </lg>
            </div>
            <p xml:lang="en">
            <lb n="3"/>End :—
            </p>
            <div n="100">
                <lg type="verse" xml:id="v_100">
                    <l>
<lb n="4"/>sve sve kāle 'tikoṣāsvaguṇavibhavataḥ kṣiptadoṣākaraśrīḥ
<caesura/>
<lb n="5"/>śaśvadviṣṇoḥ pade 'pi sphuraṇamahimato darśanyantī vilāsān |
                    </l>
                    <l>
<lb n="6"/>uddhāro jaṃbhamānya pradhanaparicaye sainadīyā kṛpāṇo
<caesura/>
<lb n="7"/>niṣkārpaṇyāhitānāṃ hṛdi vasatu haṭhākṛṣṭatatkīrttilakṣmīḥ ||
                    </l>
                </lg>
             </div>
             <p xml:lang="en">
             <lb n="8"/>Colophon :—
             </p>
             <div type="colophon">
                <p>
<lb n="9"/>iti śrīkarpaṭopanāma-vināyakabhaṭṭaviracitaḥ khaḍgaśatakam samāptamam ||
                </p>
             </div>
        </body></text></TEI>